<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="plone">

<head>
    <metal:javascript fill-slot="javascript_head_slot" tal:omit-tag="">
        <script type="text/javascript"
            tal:attributes="src string:${context/absolute_url}/++theme++ploneorg.theme/components/zaccordion/js/jquery.zaccordion.min.js">
        </script>
        <script>
          $("#slider").zAccordion({
            width: 1140,
            speed: 600,
            slideClass: "slider",
            slideWidth: 800,
            height: 400
          });
        </script>
    </metal:javascript>
</head>

<body>

  <metal:block fill-slot="top_slot"
                   tal:define="disable_column_one python:request.set('disable_plone.leftcolumn',1);
                               disable_column_two python:request.set('disable_plone.rightcolumn',1);
                               dummy python:request.set('disable_border',1)" />

  <metal:content-core fill-slot="main">

    <ul id="slider">
      <li>
        <img src="++theme++ploneorg.theme/img/examples/images/slide0.gif" width="800" height="400" alt="" />
        <div class="slider-bg"></div>
        <div class="slider-info">
          <strong>Lorem ipsum</strong>
          <p class="slider-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras porttitor lacus sollicitudin ligula sagittis a ultricies nulla ultricies. Ut odio nisi, posuere sed blandit at, bibendum non dolor.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <img src="++theme++ploneorg.theme/img/examples/images/slide1.gif" width="800" height="400" alt="" />
        <div class="slider-bg"></div>
        <div class="slider-info">
          <strong>Dolor Sit</strong>
          <p class="slider-text">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras in condimentum sem. Aenean faucibus dignissim auctor. In ut libero vitae augue laoreet iaculis at a tellus.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <img src="++theme++ploneorg.theme/img/examples/images/slide2.gif" width="800" height="400" alt="" />
        <div class="slider-bg"></div>
        <div class="slider-info">
          <strong>Donec Ultrices</strong>
          <p class="slider-text">Duis viverra velit orci. Sed vestibulum mi nec est imperdiet sed ullamcorper augue molestie. Donec ultrices facilisis erat at porttitor.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <img src="++theme++ploneorg.theme/img/examples/images/slide3.gif" width="800" height="400" alt="" />
        <div class="slider-bg"></div>
        <div class="slider-info">
          <strong>Est Imper</strong>
          <p class="slider-text">Phasellus sed lectus nisl, eget cursus eros. Suspendisse posuere orci eu lorem luctus et porta nunc posuere. Cras sed lectus vitae leo accumsan adipiscing.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>

<div class="homepage">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <p class="large-paragraph"><strong>300</strong> solution providers in <strong>57</strong> countries developing <strong>40</strong> languages</p>
      <div class="boxed boxed-stripes">Get Plone <strong>4.2.1</strong>New Collections, Diazo Theming, HTML5 Support <a class="btn" href="#">Download now</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h2>The Plone community</h2>
      <p class="large-paragraph">The plone community protects and promotes Plone. <strong>We can't do it without you!</strong></p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="boxed boxed-pill boxed-primary">
            <h3>Today's downloads</h3>
            <p class="large-paragraph"><strong>102</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="boxed boxed-pill boxed-primary">
            <h3>New tickets today</h3>
            <p class="large-paragraph"><strong>82</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="boxed boxed-pill boxed-primary">
            <h3>Commits last week</h3>
            <p class="large-paragraph"><strong>12</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="boxed boxed-pill boxed-primary">
            <h3>Release blockers</h3>
            <p class="large-paragraph"><strong>7</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="boxed boxed-pill boxed-primary">
            <h3>Open pull requests</h3>
            <p class="large-paragraph"><strong>86</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="boxed boxed-pill boxed-primary">
            <h3>Patches needing reviews</h3>
            <p class="large-paragraph"><strong>3</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="boxed">
            <h3>Plone Fundation</h3>
            <a class="large-link link-arrow">Protect and <br />promote Plone</a>
            <p>Our goal is to ensure that Plone remains the premier open soure content management system</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="boxed">
            <h3>Documentation</h3>
            <a class="large-link link-arrow">New to Plone? <br />Start here!</a>
            <ul class="list-arrows">
              <li>Installing plone</li>
              <li>Installing plone</li>
              <li>Installing plone</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="boxed boxed-primary">
            <h3>Work with us</h3>
            <a class="large-link link-arrow">Arnhem 2012</a>
            <p>Our goal is to ensure that Plone remains the premier open soure content management system</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3>Latest News</h3>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a class="medium-link link-arrow">Plone Framework Team accepts new members</a><time>Nov 08, 2012</time></li>
            <li><a class="medium-link link-arrow">Security vulnerability: 20121106 Multiple vectors</a><time>Nov 08, 2012</time></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3>Upcoming Events</h3>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li tal:repeat="event view/get_events">
              <a class="medium-link link-arrow"
                 tal:attributes="href event/getURL"
                 tal:content="event/Title">
                63rd Plone Tune-up day
              </a>
              <time tal:content="python:context.toLocalizedTime(event.start)">Nov 08, 2012</time></li>
            <!-- <li><a class="medium-link link-arrow">63rd Plone Tune-up day</a><time>Nov 08, 2012</time></li> -->
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3>Work Teams</h3>
          <a>Join and participate in the activities of our teams</a>
          <h3>Mailing Lists</h3>
          <a>Ask questions, discuss Plone, and get useful tips</a>
          <h3>Chat Room</h3>
          <a>You can chat with other Plone people and developers</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</metal:content-core>

</body>
</html>
